------------------------------------------------------
simon-0.1-alpha-1
Documentation: INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
------------------------------------------------------



0. Requirements
---------------

To successfully compile simon you need:
qt >= 4.3.* (there have been reported problems with qt-4.3.1)

Linux:
	alsa-dev
	x11-dev
WIN32:
	DirectX SDK




1. Compilation
--------------

To compile this version just issue:

$ qmake 
$ make

The binary will be put in the bin/ subdirectory (altough that might vary depending on your compiler - possible other locations include release/bin and debug/bin).



2. Configuration
--------------

When first running simon it will prompt for some essential configuration. Simon ships with some defaults located in the model/ directory.
